codynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/39967/', '', 'Acetylsalicylic acid, Naloxone, Ibuprofen, Naltrexone', 'Melatonin, Nitrazepam, Zopiclone, Valerian, Fenfluramine, Perampanel, Eslicarbazepine, Lacosamide, Stiripentol', 1767369485);
